{"tid":1188612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】新地郭基煇：歡迎修例　相信對集團無影響","createTime":"2019-06-06T11:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:16:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6b9232b6d32be95d24fdee5bb62eb116c278f6","tid":1188612,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190606/s00001/b8d55dbfefcaec786db1282770295294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190606%2Fs00001%2Fb8d55dbfefcaec786db1282770295294.jpg&h=9bab5a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》爭議不絕。新地執董、郭炳江兒子郭基煇透過發言人表示歡迎修例，並相信修例對集團無影響。<br />\n<br />\n郭基煇稱，留意到最近政府就修訂草案作出一些修改，認為修改顯示了政府回應社會意見的誠意，相信有助進一步釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n郭基煇又期望各方在尊重「一國兩制」前提下，以理性和客觀態度討論修訂《逃犯條例》，呼籲各界以務實態度排除分歧，尋找共識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190606/s00001/1559812743676/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190606%2Fs00001%2F1559812743676%2F&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=8028c9e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190606%2Fs00001%2F1559812743676%2F&h=8c45c543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190606/s00001/1559812743676/</a>"},{"pid":"b165f6cf3cddf88837a369b7fb69ca90baf7b282","tid":1188612,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5342ddafa4fe9ba4a066cecaf07dd2d06e9f6f1","tid":1188612,"uid":170249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:16:55.000Z","msg":"開刀補血 靠商人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del>支持</del>逃犯條例通過"}]}